{"tid":315634,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[7月新番]異世界食堂 第2話","createTime":"2017-07-10T07:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T01:22:20.000Z","uid":7307,"like":25,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0ea267c2da22326d412aa16427e3eeabdc8fc88","tid":315634,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:16:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/074335_4741d22af006de9f837b0a90c71ecf63.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F074335_4741d22af006de9f837b0a90c71ecf63.JPG&h=d4fd78f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原作：犬塚惇平<br />\n原作插畫：榎波克[/img]己<br />\n監督、系列構成：神保昌登<br />\n人物設定：佐野隆雄、佐野惠一<br />\n道具設定：森木靖泰<br />\n美術監督：片平真司<br />\n色彩設計：水本志保<br />\n攝影監督：佐藤敦<br />\n編輯：近藤勇二<br />\n音樂：辻林美穂／TOMISIRO<br />\n音樂製作：Flying DOG<br />\n音響監督：土屋雅紀<br />\n音響製作：grooove<br />\n動畫製作：SILVER LINK.<br />\nCAST<br />\n店主：諏訪部順一<br />\n阿蕾塔：上坂堇<br />\n黑：大西沙織<br />\n紅色女王：伊藤靜<br />\n阿爾多琉斯：清川元夢<br />\n辰五郎：大塚芳忠<br />\n阿爾馮斯：立木文彥<br />\n莎拉：安野希世乃<br />\n海因里希：杉田智和[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n放送時間:<br />\nテレビ東京: 日本深夜1:35 <br />\nbilibili:深夜1:35 <br />\nviu:<a href=\"http://www.viu.com/ott/hk/zh-hk/vod/53326/%E7%95%B0%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E9%A3%9F%E5%A0%82#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.viu.com%2Fott%2Fhk%2Fzh-hk%2Fvod%2F53326%2F%25E7%2595%25B0%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%25A0%2582%23&d=HAPa5dXP9WoaLJ2U5vHgddibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=fa7a2df9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.viu.com/ott/hk/zh-hk/vod/53326/%E7%95%B0%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E9%A3%9F%E5%A0%82#</a><br />\n<br />\nOP是由Wake Up,May』n！以「一生一次」為主題，結合本作劇情創作出的，描繪了溫暖人心的相遇的《One In A Billion》（8月9日發售）。ED是安野希世乃單飛後的第一張迷你專輯《涙。》（7月26日發售）<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/081851_997a717f05a57092790025ce35fdb022.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F081851_997a717f05a57092790025ce35fdb022.jpg&h=9536897b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/081856_50281f49f50005be34f1a830ac079b6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F081856_50281f49f50005be34f1a830ac079b6b.jpg&h=9069bf8d&s={SIZE}\" />[/quote]"},{"pid":"19317674556b70792dfc7c322472a898b7f8b5ed","tid":315634,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DEOYgbrU0AEzWjb.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDEOYgbrU0AEzWjb.jpg%3Alarge&h=790bacab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第2話: 炸肉餅 炸蝦"},{"pid":"5cd78f6e204c244a2e7c2bb060db1ae1d464b78b","tid":315634,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:17:18.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"8f3d3c35b5aad46fba828e3d7896edd8899eff30","tid":315634,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:25:57.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"c2ad73013761a011127d9629b897f71bcd13d27f","tid":315634,"uid":19232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:28:51.000Z","msg":"你已正評了這討論"},{"pid":"cef20a7f99b5f4602cab05ffebb313f608d5aea8","tid":315634,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:29:54.000Z","msg":"今集安野出場<br />\n唔知幾時先有黑睇"},{"pid":"baae1cacb1959296b423f77e9946c85df269fd2a","tid":315634,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:07:16.000Z","msg":"想助養阿蕾塔"},{"pid":"8bee6eee10a09de3d579ddab77ef53c6e58a4dae","tid":315634,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:10:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想助養阿蕾塔</blockquote><br />\n去侍奉國家工作啦"},{"pid":"ae1f55321077da419b943b2946315b5ad5d2f5cb","tid":315634,"uid":17776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:16:39.000Z","msg":"今集係咪要正評平衡返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea1466b07555bbd3c9326015a716f8de19b95dc","tid":315634,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:18:28.000Z","msg":"早排睇簡介套野好似幾特別"},{"pid":"aa3bb00e82f4f3bb61cb6b1d2e4fa0c3a6b0c0e5","tid":315634,"uid":22651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:30:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今集係咪要正評平衡返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經有一個負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42752908e921c00d357dbd62ea5a52a479e2bd8","tid":315634,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:56:05.000Z","msg":"阿蕾塔留俾你地 黑我帶走<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/10/165535_9a33cd0761bdfa3f83652a764421421f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F10%2F165535_9a33cd0761bdfa3f83652a764421421f.jpg&h=1ca3c141&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8ff4a2b626c4c46a6bbe4b68544878714af9d98","tid":315634,"uid":11154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T09:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"736947c71c57a685a931dd243c364dbb0146cf72","tid":315634,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T09:00:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿蕾塔留俾你地 黑我帶走<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/10/165535_9a33cd0761bdfa3f83652a764421421f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F10%2F165535_9a33cd0761bdfa3f83652a764421421f.jpg&h=1ca3c141&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n黑係我架<br />\n立即學煮咖喱"},{"pid":"ac9f7e4ce1a67e3a522d99befaf549f4e9cdb3dc","tid":315634,"uid":19232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T12:07:18.000Z","msg":"Q：前幾天動畫的第一集播出了，那麼請談談感想吧。<br />\n<br />\n上坂堇（阿蕾塔役）：阿蕾塔是迷了路、誤打誤撞來到這兒的，而動畫將角色刻畫得更加可愛了。畢竟音響導演當時也跟我說：&ldquo;配音的時候，要充分顯現出她快要餓死的樣子。&rdquo;畢竟她因為太過於飢餓的關係，大腦都不能好好地運轉了哦。這跟原作不同，是動畫原創的劇情，不過對我而言，則是一個非常慘烈的開始了。<br />\n<br />\n伊藤靜（紅色女王役）：我的感想就是：&ldquo;啊，開始了嗎。這個深夜報復社會的番（笑）。&rdquo;光是在配音的時候聽到大家的演技，就讓我覺得肚子餓了呢。儘管錄音的時候沒有畫面，可是大家的對話已經能夠誘發肚子咕咕叫了，因此我非常期待完成版到底會是什麼樣的效果。<br />\n<br />\n強強對話！政委&amp;靜御前談《異世界食堂》<br />\n<br />\nQ：那麼兩位對第一集當中的劇情，是否有什麼特別喜歡的內容呢？<br />\n<br />\n上坂：導演說這部作品的主人公是&ldquo;料理&rdquo;。不過在剛開始的時候，異世界的人卻在那兒一邊吃一邊進行各種解說，這讓我印象深刻。明明不知道原材料是啥，卻會覺得很好吃呢。至於阿蕾塔的話，此前都是一天只能吃個男爵果實來度日呢。<br />\n<br />\n伊藤：（哭腔）嗚嗚，好可憐的女孩子&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n上坂：另外在店主的要求下，阿蕾塔去洗了個澡，這一幕也讓我受到了很大衝擊。畢竟身上的污漬都被清晰地畫出來了。本來以為只是報復社會的美食番，沒想到如此寫實啊&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nQ：確實，一般而言洗澡的劇情應該都是送福利才對&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n伊藤：感覺隨著角色視角的不同，彷彿作品也發生了變化呢。不過食物的魅力依然非常了得。包括紅色女王在內，所有的角色在談到料理時都非常有熱情，這也刺激了觀眾的食慾。說起來，在第一集的配音結束之後，我在趕往下一個片場的路上就覺得無論如何都要吃點東西，於是就跑去家庭餐館點了份燉牛肉吃呢。<br />\n<br />\nQ：在閱讀原作跟實際配音之後，兩位對作品的印像是否也有不同呢？<br />\n<br />\n上坂：雖然打著&ldquo;異世界&rdquo;的旗號，不過對阿蕾塔跟紅色女王而言，貓屋才是真正的異世界。並非是現代的日本人去異世界，而是異世界的人過來接觸日本的文化，這一點很有趣呢。另外聲優陣容非常豪華。來自異世界的都是什麼賢者、劍豪或者大商人，為此豪華的聲優陣容也讓他們顯得更加有厚重感了。不過在食堂當中，所有人都是平等的，即便有爭吵，但還是會享受美味的飯菜呢。<br />\n<br />\n伊藤：紅色女王可是龍啊，而且後面應該還會有各種各樣的客人登場，那麼我就在想：&ldquo;沒問題吧？&rdquo;（笑）在各種不同的環境當中，不同的人聚集在一起聊天，這非常有趣。將這一切聯繫在一起的貓屋太厲害了，連我都忍不住想要去看看呢。<br />\n<br />\n強強對話！政委&amp;靜御前談《異世界食堂》<br />\n<br />\nQ：那麼兩位對自己配音角色的印像如何呢？首先是阿蕾塔。<br />\n<br />\n上坂：阿蕾塔在工作的時候被人識破了魔族的身份，然後丟了工作。在這種情況下被店主僱用，然後開始在貓屋工作了。在異國他鄉面對不熟悉的料理，她卻拼命要記住這些知識。吃飯的樣子非常可愛，基本上沒有挑食的情況。另外她很適合女僕裝，不過店主居然真的能給她準備女僕裝啊&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n強強對話！政委&amp;靜御前談《異世界食堂》<br />\n<br />\nQ：那麼，關於紅色女王呢？<br />\n<br />\n伊藤：平時因為是女王，所以顯得威風凜凜，不過每週都非常期待去貓屋，並且無法抵抗燉牛肉的魅力。總之我也是非常用心，帶著愛去展現她享受美味的姿態。<br />\n<br />\nQ：如果跟作品一樣，用料理的名字來稱呼自己的話，兩位覺得自己是什麼料理呢？<br />\n<br />\n上坂：應該是最喜歡的料理吧？那麼我就是蛋包飯了。我特別喜歡蛋包飯，經常去吃呢。<br />\n<br />\n伊藤：我就是意大利玉棋之類的吧。<br />\n<br />\n強強對話！政委&amp;靜御前談《異世界食堂》<br />\n<br />\nQ：那麼最後，請給大家說幾句話吧。<br />\n<br />\n上坂：這是一部充滿了幸福感的作品，沒有人會受傷，可以靜下心來觀看作品。還請大家繼續悠哉地期待作品，將其作為生活的伴侶，每過七天享受一次樂趣吧。<br />\n<br />\n伊藤：在小堇說完之後，我還能說啥呢。 &ldquo;承蒙招待？&rdquo;（笑）毫無疑問，看完之後肯定有幸福的感覺。如果你是吃貨，或者喜歡做料理的話，還請駐足於貓屋吧。作品也會將美味跟幸福分享給大家的。"},{"pid":"c5f3a5a0fc3e16803c563cdd1c3144dd5f85f7fd","tid":315634,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:39:57.000Z","msg":"B站更左"},{"pid":"e4923cd8922fbc95bf47dfcacc0f536ccca53696","tid":315634,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:45:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>B站更左</blockquote><br />\nviu 2點左右更新 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23438b9e73d3ddd31e8f4e1fa61e387dab6505b","tid":315634,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:48:41.000Z","msg":"肉繹不絕餅果然好食過 上集個早餐"},{"pid":"2551b3307c02eb986c824afb78aa061a0add776a","tid":315634,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:48:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肉繹不絕餅果然好食過 上集個早餐</blockquote><br />\n肉餅"},{"pid":"a0e7971091b230e75bc16ba1be9a352b7b83e35b","tid":315634,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T18:01:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>肉繹不絕餅果然好食過 上集個早餐</blockquote><br />\n肉餅</blockquote><br />\n諗緊臨訓睇定聽朝睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb4ed44675094091916172936e16b20f0147590b","tid":315634,"uid":52590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T18:01:48.000Z","msg":"即將播放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e5e3ce51a586d30596d2a64dd94c3392770794","tid":315634,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T18:04:11.000Z","msg":"下集仲未有黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60b635c668de5b9af8559025710c934377360b1","tid":315634,"uid":52590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T18:09:23.000Z","msg":"有喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144fd5f2c62e9fe370fbebfc4a1697440ac09503",